show.description: Ines, jilted by the wealthy Ward family, had a one-night stand with a male escort due to her cousin's scheme. That same night, her broke father committed suicide. Fleeing Los Angeles in disgrace, she returned four years later with her son, Charlie. At SKY CLUB, she recognized the escort by his tattoo and demanded compensation, forcing him into a debt repayment agreement. Meanwhile, her company's CEO, Louis, mysteriously targeted her, leaving Ines puzzled about their past connection.
